Sample.Title: VREI_A006_7-24-01
Sample.Description: TP05 late L4 prep 1 hermaphrodites vs mixed reference

Column.Name: CH1_median
Column.Description: Channel 1 (635 nm, Cy5, Reference) median pixel intensity

Column.Name: CH2_median
Column.Description: Channel 2 (532 nm, Cy3, Experiment) median pixel intensity

Column.Name: CH1_back
Column.Description: Channel 1 Background

Column.Name: CH2_back
Column.Description: Channel 2 Background

Column.Name: CH1_MEAN
Column.Description: Channel 1 Mean

Column.Name: CH1_SD
Column.Description: Channel 1 Standard Deviation

Column.Name: CH2_SD
Column.Description: Channel 2 Standard Deviation

Column.Name: pixels
Column.Description: Number of pixels used to determine signal.

Column.Name: bpixels
Column.Description: Number of pixels used to determine background.

Column.Name: x
Column.Description: X-coordinate of the center of the feature-indicator associated with the feature, where (0,0) is the top left of the image

Column.Name: y
Column.Description: Y-coordinate of the center of the feature-indicator associated with the feature, where (0,0) is the top left of the image

Column.Name: diameter
Column.Description: diameter in µm of the feature-indicator

Column.Name: %>CH1_back+1SD
Column.Description: percentage of feature pixels with intensities more than one standard deviation above the background pixel intensity, for Channel 1

Column.Name: %>CH1_back+2SD
Column.Description: percentage of feature pixels with intensities more than two standard deviations above the background pixel intensity, for Channel 1

Column.Name: %>CH2_back+1SD
Column.Description: percentage of feature pixels with intensities more than one standard deviation above the background pixel intensity, for Channel 2

Column.Name: %>CH2_back+2SD
Column.Description: percentage of feature pixels with intensities more than two standard deviations above the background pixel intensity, for Channel 2

Column.Name: CH1_%Sat
Column.Description: percentage of pixel saturation within feature for Channel 1

Column.Name: CH2_%Sat
Column.Description: percentage of pixel saturation within feature for Channel 2

Column.Name: flag
Column.Description: An extension of GenePix 3.0 flags described at http://twiki.med.yale.edu/twiki/bin/view/YMD/YMDFlagFields

Column.Name: ratio_calc
Column.Description: (CH1_median-CH1_back)/(CH2_median-CH2_back)

Column.Name: VALUE
Column.Description: log ratio (log2 of PRE_VALUE)

Column.Name: norm_factor
Column.Description: Normalization factor calculated as described at http://twiki.med.yale.edu/twiki/bin/view/YMD/NormalizationAndFilterMethods

Column.Name: PRE_VALUE
Column.Description: [(Experiment channel median intensity - background)/(Reference channel median intensity - background)]*(norm_factor)
